dublin_core.dcvalue: Traditionally health educators have provided contraception counseling highlighting long acting reversible contraceptive LARC methods Recently mobile health applications have gained attention as potentially effective communicative tools We designed a mobile application Plan A Birth Control Plan ABC to provide tailored information about the most common nonpermanent contraceptive methods with emphasis on LARC methods
Made available in DSpace on 2020-02-06T19:04:08Z (GMT). No. of bitstreams: 0 Previous issue date: 2014-04-28
Mobile health application for long-acting reversible contraceptive information: a secondary analysis.
